    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>与最多4位好友在多人模式中击败成群的敌人：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116260/extras/22a82d357a46a733ef6364c27fdd7e75.poster.avif?t=1768407945\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116260/extras/22a82d357a46a733ef6364c27fdd7e75.webm?t=1768407945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116260/extras/22a82d357a46a733ef6364c27fdd7e75.mp4?t=1768407945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>收集遗物，变得更强，并创建构建来协同你的力量：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116260/extras/f17242033a1c09ce67036a736142b775.poster.avif?t=1768407945\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116260/extras/f17242033a1c09ce67036a736142b775.webm?t=1768407945\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2116260/extras/f17242033a1c09ce67036a736142b775.mp4?t=1768407945\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>特点：</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 单人游戏或在线多人游戏，最多支持4名玩家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 超过30种独特遗物和10种被动升级。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 多个关卡和首领战。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >• 可解锁角色。</p>",
